item.title: CVE-2022-4370|2024-08-03T01:34:50.125Z -- unknown -- multimedial%20images
item.description: The multimedial images WordPress plugin through 1.0b does not properly sanitize and escape a parameter before using it in a SQL statement, leading to a SQL injection exploitable by users with a role as low as Admin.
